ygData.messageBody:
I cannot help but say... yeppers. Sorry Zinf, but
yes. I always assume guy unless they tell me they're a
girl. Course, I occasionally flirt with them anyway b/c
flirting with a girl or a guy doesn't matter if it's all
online and no consequence.<br><br>Course, I flirt b/c
it's funny and entertaining. And it passes Downtime on
EQ quickly. Heh. It also makes ya fun to group with.
And I'm addicted to groups. No EQ really unless I
group. Course it's been hard to find EQ time lately.
*sighs like the breeze*<br><br>shooman
out...<br>Fatedhue Prismatic of the Drinal Server<br>(Druid of
course... why else would I sigh like a breeze?
lol)<br><br>PS... Zinfandel White... cool nick! And heh, just got
reminded by some poster from England that ppl other than
those in the US play.<br><br>But darned that must be
expensive cause I hear in the UK and other locations,
Internet access is paid for by the minute over there
still.<br><br>shoomie out (I'm not bad, I'm just drawn that way!)
